Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on June 8, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
S.B. NO. 2061, S.D. 2, H.D. 2, RELATING TO RESIDENTIAL CONDOMINIUMS.
